lines.text: I'm glad I'm just a pussy!
He's got an awfully nice speaking voice when he's not pretending to be common.
Oooh, it's not the sort of place I could afford to be seen in after I'm famous Brenda. Shouldn't think they've even heard of scampi.
I'll go up to Carnaby Street by myself. Find a flat, get a modeling job, then I'll come back and get you.
If I'm going to be famous I've got to have smart luggage!
I'll just have to tell them I hadn't the facilities available to achieve the new switched-on casual look.
